headline: Forge Global and ICE to Bring Greater Transparency to Private Markets with Forge Price™
summary: NEW YORK & SAN FRANCISCO, April 22, 2025--Forge Global Holdings, Inc. ("Forge") (NYSE: FRGE), a leading provider of marketplace infrastructure, data services, and technology and investment solutions for the private market, today announced an agreement with Intercontinental Exchange (NYSE: ICE), a leading global provider of data and technology, to distribute Forge Price™, a novel proprietary pricing dataset for private company equity.
